\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 And you're a widow?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Can you tell me the year of your marriage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 1924.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 And the year of your birth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 1900.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Where were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Darlington.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 How many years did you live in the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 About seven.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Where was that?
