\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes, we - well we used to see them - pretty regular. You know, they - they used to come to Darlington and we used to go to Stockton.
