\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Perhaps maybe - every two month or so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 You say your auntie had relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 In Darlington.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 And at Eryholme?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes.
