\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Did your mother have friends of her own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes.
