\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Well her husband was the - Cleveland Bridge yard. And - eyes, an
d they were - went off on jobs together and were near together - near to each other. Yes.
