\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Can you think of any sort of people who belonged to a different class from yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No, I didn't mix with - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Can you remember being brought up to treat people of one sort differently from people of another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Were you ever told to curtsey or show respect in some way to anybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Was there anyone you called sir or master or madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Not in my time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Do you remember anyone showing respect to your parents or your auntie in these ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 In Darlington who were considered the most important people at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Well - the M.P. wouldn't we. Wasn't it Pike Pease.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Anybody else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 You just remember the M.P.?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Did you come into contact with him at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 
Just - when we went down the market place, I went down with my father to the market place there, the election. They were giving the results.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 What was his name?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Pease. Pike Pease. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Why do you think he was considered important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Well he did - the Peas's did a lot for Darlington then didn't they. I think that's how -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Who did the shopkeepers associate with, who did they have for friends in Darlington? Did you ever notice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Did you know any shopkeepers particularly?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 We had a - as from 19 - up to 1918. Well I - was a confectioner at Robinsons, would that be any ....?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 You were before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Well who would you have for friends, who do you think the shopkeepers had for friends in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Well I don't know whether - what - who the shopkeepers had for friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 You never noticed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 What about the clergy, who do you think they associated with, who did they have for friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Well it should be the congregation shouldn't they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Was it, did they mix well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Well I did - I don't know. I don't think - some of them do really. You can put a query with that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Who would the teachers have for friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Well - the - the scholars, they should have shouldn't they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 And the farmers, who would they associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 The - oh well, the - when they went to boy cattle and - buyers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 They'd be friendly with the buyers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 And the people who were in the same business?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Same. The cattle.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 And the employers, who do you think they associated with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Well they should be friendly with their employees shouldn't they.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Were they at Cleveland Bridge, did the management mix in with the men at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 I couldn't - tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 What sort of people would you say went to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Well just the ordinary - and some business people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 And who went to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Well the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 There was no difference between the type of people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 
Where you lived did all the people in the working class have the same standard of living or would you say there were different groups within the working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Well - some were better managers weren't they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Better managers in what way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 
In - their money going - spending their money and feeding the family differently. Getting plain good food. Where some just used to - well they - hadn't any - some didn't - bother really did they. They were hard times those - in those 
days some of them. 'Cos - there was once - it was my birthday, there - everyone that was out on strike and we had nothing in the house. This was when I was at home. And - my aunt at London sent - a big box of cakes and a birthday cake in, or else we would
n't have had much to eat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Because things were so bad?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 So even in the working class you found that some families were poorer than others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Could you describe one of these poor families? Was there any particular family that you knew that seemed a bit poorer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No, I couldn't remember, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 You just think they didn't manage their money as well?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No. No. Some didn't, no. Well there wasn't much to manage on those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Do you think that one group felt itself superior to the rest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Well - not that I mixed with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Were some families thought of as rough and others as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Which type of family was thought of as rough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Well - the men that used to go to the - the pubs every night and come home drunk and leave their wives short.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Because they were drinking the money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Which do you think were the respectable ones then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Well - gave their wives the money - to keep the house going.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Do you remember a distinction of this kind between craftsmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No. I - well I didn't notice it. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Did your mother and father have the same attitude to people in different classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a particular social class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 
Well - she was - no I don't think so. She was just - just an ordinary working woman. Working class. But she was brought up - in a religious family. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Why do you think she saw herself as belonging to the working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Because she had to work for a living. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Was it possible at that time to move from one class to another and can you remember anyone who did, moved sort of up the social scale?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No, I can't remember it, no.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Do you remember anyone being described as a real gentleman or a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Well my mother and father always used to say Pike Pease was a real gentleman.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Why do you think that was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Because he was kind. Yes. Because me father came in contact with him. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 How would that he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 
I don't know how but he did - he once - well me father, I don't know how old I would be but - when me father was retired and he wasn't working at the Cleveland Bridge yard he brought my father a turkey. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 And he was a kind man was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Do you remember seeing a policeman round where you lived as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 What did you think of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Well - he was - he was all right. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 You weren't frightened of him or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No. 
But there was one who was a proper bully. Yes. I don't know what they - there was a boy, he was sat on the railing like that, as that was, and he fell into a cornfield and - he took him and he got the birch. He - he got the birch, yes, and he - a quieter 
boy you couldn't have come across. I forget the - what they called that policeman. Carr I think they called him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Just because he'd fallen into a cornfield?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Jacky Curry they called him. And he said he was playing in the cornfield but he wasn't. Bu
t he wouldn't take any of our statements, he just - caught the boy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 So you didn't like him very much?
