\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 For what offences would you be caned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Well if you were late for school. Or if you disbehaved yourself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Did your auntie or your mother show an interest in your schoolwork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Did they ask what you did at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No. Don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Did they visit the school or did they ever meet the teachers.?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 At Dodmire Street did the other children come from similar types of home to your own or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from the others at Dodmire Street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Were there any gangs or groups in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Were there any children who were left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Not that I noticed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Did you go to another school afterwards or was this the last one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 That was the last school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 How old would you be when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Fourteen.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Would you have stayed longer if you'd had the opportunity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 You didn't like it that much then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Did you attend any part time education after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Do you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 
No. Well I have really. I wasn't very good at school really. And I wish I had been clever and - because it helps you a lot if you've had a good education, yes. When you hear peo
ple speaking you think, oh how nice. Can speak about anything, any subject and you feel out of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Do you think you benefitted from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No, I don't think so. But then I wasn't - I wasn't bright.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 When you first went to your auntie you lived in King William Street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 King William Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 And you were there about three and a half years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Three to three and a half. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 And then you went to Stockton for a holiday and what happened then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 And - I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 You had an accident?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes, had an accident.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Can you describe this accident?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 
Well I was - asked aunt if I could clean the windows and she put the steps for - right for me, and I altered them and fell off - onto the back of my head. And I was take
n to Stockton hospital, childrens hospital, and I was unconscious for three weeks. And - they thought I would either be blind or silly. Yes. So - I got over it and still have - I don't think I'm silly.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 That's why you changed schools then was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes. Because - they thought it was a long way for me to walk. When we moved to Falmer Road. And Dodmire school was near at hand. Yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 So you'd be in Falmer Road then about three and a half years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 So you never lived in a house as a child longer than three and a half years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 While you were at school did you have a part time job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Or any way of earning a little regular money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 What was your first full time job when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Oh - wel
l I wanted to be a confection - a confectioner. And there wasn't a vacancy, I put my name down to different - establishments so I did odd jobs. I was in - Piper's Bazaar. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Like a shop assistant was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes. And Hill's Bazaar. And I was at - 
Robinsons - that's a gents shop, writing envelopes to send circulars out. And then - another chap and I - we went out giving the circulars out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 For Robinsons?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes. And I was at Tysons' in Houndgate. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 What did you do there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yo
u won't believe it when I tell you, packing salt and washing soda. Packing. Yes. And then - and after that I got into - Robinsons. Confectioners shop in - Coniscliff Road.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 How old would you be then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Oh - about six - sixteen. 1916. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 And these other jobs would only before a short time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes. Yes. Just filling in time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 An at the end of 1918 were you still in Robinsons, did you stay in the confectioners shop then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 I left - now when did the war finish, 1918. Well I left about
 six month - before the war finished and went into - Stephenson's munitions - munition works. And I was there about six month and then - I went back to -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 To Robinsons?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 And you stayed there did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 The first job you had then was with Piper's Bazaars as a shop assistant?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 How did you get that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Just went and made enquiries if they wanted any assistants.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 How long were you there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Oh - perhaps about a year and a half.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 What exactly did you have to do in this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Well it was just a bazaar like - Woolworth's is now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 And you were a shop assistant?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 What hours did you work there, can you remember?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 From - nine - well what time did they close at the night then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 They used to work late didn't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes. About - 'til eight did they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 It'd be a long day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 They were long days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Did you work on Sunday or Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No. Saturday. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Was it a full day on Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Did you have any half days at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Wednesday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Just a half day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Did you have any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Do you remember what you were paid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No idea at all what you got?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Do you remember if you felt it was a fair wage or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 No I don't remember. I was only fourteen you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1535777 EL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 All of it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795916 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1070193\charrsid7160315 You went to live at home then didn't you?
